import React from 'react'
import {Card, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'
// import asd from '../resources'
function Product({product}) {
  return (
    <Card style={{ width: '18rem', height: '30rem'}} className='my-3  rounded'>
        <Card.Body>
            <Card.Img className='mb-3'src={require(`../resources/05.jpg`)}/>
            <Card.Title>{product.name}</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>
                {product.description}
            </Card.Text>
            <Card.Text>
                Cena: {product.price} / t
            </Card.Text>
            <Button variant="primary" href={`/product/${product.id}`}>Zobacz</Button>
        </Card.Body>
    </Card> 
  )
}

export default Product
